ause%20Ansell%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bticking%20time%20bomb%20of%20cuteness.%26quot%3B%20He%20hopes%20the%20series%20will%20give%20him%20the%20chance%20to%20chart%20Egg's%20coming-of-age%20story%2C%20to%20confront%20the%20tenderness%20and%20brutality%20of%20growing%20up%20that%20are%20universal%20whether%20you're%20in%20Westeros%20or%20the%20real%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20what%20point%20does%20the%20person%20start%20becoming%20responsible%20for%20who%20they%20are%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20function%20of%20the%20environment%20that%20they%20were%20brought%20up%20in%3F%26quot%3B%20Parker%20hinted%2C%20wondering%20aloud.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20we're%20finding%20Egg%20just%20right%20at%20that%20turning%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fknight-of-the-seven-kingdoms-game-of-thrones-review-showrunner-interview-2026-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1768570981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F696577ab764ca5f34d2a4fb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fknight-of-the-seven-kingdoms-game-of-thrones-review-showrunner-interview-2026-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BA%20Knight%20of%20the%20Seven%20Kingdoms%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20spinoff%20with%20lower%20stakes%20and%20more%20soul.%20That's%20a%20good%20thing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cahlgrim%40insider.com%20(Callie%20Ahlgrim)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fknight-of-the-seven-kingdoms-game-of-thrones-review-showrunner-interview-2026-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Danger%20Not%20To%20Marathis%2C%20But%20Their%20Parties'%20Existence%3A%20E%20Shinde%20On%20Thackerays%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Pulling%20no%20punches%20after%20his%20party%20won%20the%20BMC%20electi