chool%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20where%20the%20federal%20government%20is%20omnipresent.%20I%20was%20drawn%20to%20federal%20jobs%20not%20only%20because%20of%20the%20perceived%20security%2C%20but%20because%20I%20felt%20they%20mattered.%20With%20this%20work%2C%20I%20could%20help%20people%2C%20defend%20justice%2C%20and%20protect%20the%20environment.%20After%20about%2014%20years%20as%20a%20federal%20attorney%2C%20my%20salary%20is%20about%20%24186%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2216f446d4-1de2-4418-8e85-7eba8b312df1%5C%22%3EI%20charge%20%242%2C000%20to%20write%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20cover%20letter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20reviewing%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20for%20friends%2C%20colleagues%2C%20and%20mentees%20for%20years.%20Then%2C%20in%20early%202020%2C%20one%20of%20my%20friends%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20really%20good%20at%20this.%20Have%20you%20ever%20considered%20it%20as%20a%20career%20path%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20question%20made%20me%20realize%20I%20had%20this%20latent%20talent%20that%20I'd%20never%20really%20considered%20harnessing.%20Soon%20after%2C%20the%20pandemic%20hit.%20I%20was%20used%20to%20traveling%20about%20twice%20a%20month%20for%20work%2C%20and%20when%20that%20stopped%2C%20I%20had%20time%20to%20spare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20signed%20up%20for%20Fiverr%20and%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-get-job-what-to-never-always-include-resume-hiring-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewriting%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Initially%2C%20I%20set%20my%20prices%20low%2C%20but%20I%20soon%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20emphasize%20quality%20over%20quantity.%20Today%2C%20I%20charge%20%242%2C000%20for%20a%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20cover%20letter.%20I%20spend%20many%20hours%20reviewing%20each%20client's%20history%20and%20experience%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20way%20to%20present%20them%20in%20the%20most%20favorable%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d6f04c9-4632