o%20leave%20the%20service%20during%20the%20height%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20the%20civilian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-job-search-white-collar-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20felt%20uncertain%2C%20and%20many%20encouraged%20me%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20retired%20service%20members%20who%20had%20built%20businesses%20offered%20a%20different%20message.%20They%20helped%20me%20realize%20that%20the%20military%20equips%20people%20with%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanging-jobs-skills-new-career-industry-switch-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etransferable%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20they%20often%20think.%20The%20transition%20resources%20on%20base%20reinforced%20that%20point%2C%20so%20I%20felt%20ready%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222cd2f5a-8d47-4774-b11b-a0696caa6218%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20military%20experience%20gave%20me%20options%2C%20but%20not%20a%20single%20direction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Marines%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20amphibious%20operations%20and%20rotated%20through%20several%20roles.%20That%20variety%20helped%20me%20grow%2C%20but%20it%20also%20made%20choosing%20a%20civilian%20path%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20multiple%20strengths%20and%20enjoyed%20different%20aspects%20of%20my%20job%2C%20which%20meant%20I%20didn't%20leave%20with%20a%20single%2C%20defined%20plan.%20I%20had%20possibilities%2C%20but%20no%20fixed%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20committed%20to%20transitioning%2C%20I%20wrote%20my%20goals%20down%20and%20worked%20toward%20them%20before%20my%20end%20date.%20Even%20with%20that%20preparation%2C%20the%20hardest%20part%20was%20simply%20starting.%20In%20the%20military%2C%20the%20steps%20are%20usually%20provided.%20In%20civilian%20life%2C%20you%20take%20every%20step%20on%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20feel%20directionl