%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPunjab%20is%20not%20just%20a%20state%20to%20me%3B%20it%20is%20a%20breathing%20heritage.%20The%20environmental%20challenges%20we%20face%20are%20not%20isolated%3B%20they%20are%20symptoms%20of%20a%20larger%20disconnect%20between%20communities%20and%20nature.%20Our%20work%20is%20about%20restoring%20that%20bond%2C%20nurturing%20both%20land%20and%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F474029%2Fjagdish-kuniyal-tree-planting-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%20but%20about%20cultivating%20a%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20nature%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20community%20grow%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuiding%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20afforestation%20efforts%20is%20Vishal%20Chowla%2C%20project%20lead%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20rebuild%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20by%20reintroducing%20native%20tree%20species%20to%20depleted%20landscapes.%20He%20recalls%20the%20early%20days%20vividly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20these%20villages%2C%20the%20soil%20was%20exhausted%20and%20the%20air%20heavy%20with%20pollution.%20We%20knew%20planting%20trees%20was%20essential%2C%20but%20the%20real%20challenge%20was%20to%20plant%20hope%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seed%20of%20hope%20was%20first%20sown%20in%20March%202019%2C%20when%20the%20foundation%20planted%20saplings%20on%20government%20land%20in%20Badaushi%20Kalan%2